f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011f8a6dce61267eebf8f6b0dd9c20452932c453","tid":173573,"uid":34495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學啦<br />\n上2個月先教識左個朋友踩<br />\n20分鐘就教識左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我試過圍住個場邊成個鐘都唔識</blockquote><br />\n有人幫就搵個人係隔離推住/扶住你踩，之後慢慢會學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我學果陣無人幫，一落斜就識左，我都唔知點解果陣我唔識都夠膽死沖落斜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bea7cf1a8214f1e6902086ca3358cce7e401c6","tid":173573,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學啦<br />\n上2個月先教識左個朋友踩<br />\n20分鐘就教識左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我試過圍住個場邊成個鐘都唔識</blockquote><br />\n有人幫就搵個人係隔離推住/扶住你踩，之後慢慢會學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我學果陣無人幫，一落斜就識左，我都唔知點解果陣我唔識都夠膽死沖落斜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n速度有助平衡?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a0a3a3fafa0f8ee0fc2f57660327d964796f9e","tid":173573,"uid":79037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:40:31.000Z","msg":"我18歲之前都係唔識..<br />\n讀high dip 果陣d fd 開始約星期日踩單車<br />\n我都係自學...<br />\n<br />\n22歲, 第一次環台灣成功..<br />\n26歲.. 第2次環台成功..<br />\n其實踩單車真係幾好玩.. 巴打加油"},{"pid":"6d8775bdf22188b197263670cd06f2c3aa40dde1","tid":173573,"uid":15497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識揸車仲玩踩單車?</blockquote><br />\n我唔識揸車架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我識但條女都係早我成年攞到牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf61669b1ce88aba7d32586cf544dc7a8673a7e","tid":173573,"uid":5190,"like":0,"disl